## Exercises using SELECT

1. Write a query to display the names (first_name, last_name) from the customer table

2. Write a query to display the names (first_name, last_name) using an alias name â€œFirst Name", "Last Name" from the customer table

3. Write a query to get the details of all customers from the customer table in descending order by their first name.

4. Display the first and last names of all actors from the table actor.

5. Display the first and last name of each actor in a single column in upper case letters. Name the column Actor Name.

6. You need to find the ID number, first name, and last name of an actor, of whom you know only the first name, "Joe."  What is one query would you use to obtain this information?

